SCREEN-GUARDS.title: iPhone 12 - Sheath Screen Protector with Applicator Tray
SCREEN-GUARDS.description: Screen Protector is reliable only when it aligns and fits properly onto your phone’s screen. With complete edge to edge coverage, the protector comes with an applicator tray which needs to be placed on the phone’s screen after removing the film. Afterwards, simply peel off the sticker at the back for perfect placement of the oleophobic screen guard without causing any bubbles on the screen. Saving you from the hassle, the tray offers easy application while the guard keeps the screen safe from scratches and bumps.
